headline: CrowdStrike Named a Leader and Outperformer in the 2024 GigaOm Radar Report for Ransomware Prevention
summary: AUSTIN, Texas, December 16, 2024--CrowdStrike (NASDAQ: CRWD) today announced it has been named a Leader and Outperformer in the 2024 GigaOm Radar Report for Ransomware Prevention. The report recognized the innovation and leadership of the CrowdStrike Falcon® cybersecurity platform, awarding it 10 perfect scores across critical categories, including Predictive Analytics, Data Exfiltration Protection, Response Automation, Security Ecosystem Integration and Ease of Management.
